    """
    Feature: ehime-rpg-map-topscreen, Property 5: 称号マッピングの全射性と正確性

    For any valid level (1-99), get_title SHALL return the correct title
    according to the mapping:
    - Level 1-2: "伊予の迷い人"
    - Level 3-5: "愛媛の駆け出しAI研究者"
